      • success

        Future<T> success(SuccessCallback<T> callback)
        Set a callback to be invoked when this Future completes successfully.
        参数:
        callback -
        返回:
        A future that will resolve once the success callback completes, which may contain any errors thrown by the success callback.

      • then

        Set a callback to be invoked when this Future completes successfully.
        类型参数:
        R -
        参数:
        then -
        返回:
        A future containing all exceptions that happened prior or during the callback, or the successful result.

      • fail

        Future<T> fail(FailCallback fail)
        Set a callback to be invoked when this future completes with a failure. The failure can be observered and rethrown, otherwise it is considered handled.
        参数:
        fail -
        返回:

      • failConvert

        Future<T> failConvert(FailConvertCallback<T> fail)
        Set a callback to be invoked when this future completes with a failure. The failure can be observered and rethrown, or handled by returning a new fallback value of the same type.
        参数:
        fail -
        返回:

      • failRecover

        Future<T> failRecover(FailRecoverCallback<T> fail)
        Set a callback to be invoked when this future completes with a failure. The failure should be observered and rethrown, or handled by returning a new future of the same type.
        参数:
        fail -
        返回:
